{"kind": "daily", "date": "2026-07-18", "html": "<div style=\"font-family:-apple-system,'PingFang TC','Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;color:#16213e;\">\n<div style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#1a2b4a;border-left:5px solid #5b8def;padding-left:12px;margin:0 0 18px;\">📰 每日 AI 新聞 Top 10 · 2026-07-18</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#f9edf6;border-left:5px solid #c56bb0;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#c56bb0;font-weight:800;\">1.</span> 1Password Adds Controlled Login for Claude AI Agents<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b04b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">1Password為Claude推出受控登入功能</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">1Password and Anthropic launched 1Password for Claude, letting Claude log into websites during browser tasks with user authorization while keeping passwords and OTPs hidden from the model. Credentials never enter Claude's context, memory, or Anthropic's systems.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">1Password與Anthropic合作推出1Password for Claude,讓Claude執行瀏覽器任務時可在授權下登入網站,但密碼與一次性驗證碼不會提供給模型。憑證仍由1Password保管,不進入Claude的上下文或記憶。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177407\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#eef4ff;border-left:5px solid #5b8def;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#5b8def;font-weight:800;\">2.</span> Databricks Hits $188B Valuation as AI's Favorite Second Act<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#3b6cf6;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Databricks估值飆至1,880億美元,穩坐AI熱門企業</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Databricks has remade itself into an AI company and published research on the cost savings of open-weight AI models for coding, extending its run as one of AI's most-watched enterprises.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Databricks已重塑為一家AI公司,並發表開源權重AI模型在程式撰寫上的成本效益研究,估值持續攀升。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/17/databricks-hits-188b-valuation-extending-its-run-as-ais-favorite-second-act/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#ecf7ef;border-left:5px solid #4caf72;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#4caf72;font-weight:800;\">3.</span> xAI Can't Deny Grok Makes CSAM Anymore — So It's Suing Users<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#1e9e57;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">xAI無法否認Grok生成兒少性虐待影像,轉而提告使用者</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Elon Musk's xAI has filed its first lawsuit against a Grok user accused of generating child sexual abuse material, after previously denying the chatbot could produce such content.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">馬斯克旗下xAI對一名被控利用Grok生成兒少性虐待影像的使用者提告,先前該公司曾否認聊天機器人能產出此類內容。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">Ars Technica</b> · <a href=\"https://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2026/07/xai-cant-deny-grok-makes-csam-anymore-so-its-suing-users/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#f1ecfb;border-left:5px solid #8a6bd8;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#8a6bd8;font-weight:800;\">4.</span> How Apple's Trade Secrets Lawsuit Could Disrupt OpenAI's IPO Plans<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#6b3bf6;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">蘋果提告OpenAI侵害商業機密,恐衝擊其IPO計畫</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Apple filed a trade secrets lawsuit against OpenAI, alleging misconduct reaching up to OpenAI's chief hardware officer and claiming over 400 former Apple employees now work at the company.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">蘋果對OpenAI提起商業機密訴訟,指控不當行為一路延伸至OpenAI硬體長,並指出逾400名前蘋果員工如今任職於OpenAI。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/video/how-apples-big-lawsuit-could-disrupt-openais-ipo-plans/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#e8f6f5;border-left:5px solid #2bb0a6;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#2bb0a6;font-weight:800;\">5.</span> Advanced Backdoors Daxin, Stupig Target Taiwan's Manufacturing Sector<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#0f9b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">高階後門Daxin、Stupig鎖定臺灣製造業發動攻擊</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Security researchers say the sophisticated Chinese backdoor Daxin, first exposed in 2022 with activity dating back to 2013, has now been used to attack Taiwanese manufacturers.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">資安研究人員指出,2022年曝光、活動可追溯至2013年的中國高階後門Daxin,如今遭駭客用於攻擊臺灣製造業者。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177390\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#fbf3e3;border-left:5px solid #d99b3f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#d99b3f;font-weight:800;\">6.</span> Microsoft's Just-Patched SharePoint Flaw Already Exploited in the Wild<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b9791f;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">微軟甫修補的SharePoint重大漏洞已被用於實際攻擊</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Days after CISA warned of active exploitation targeting three known SharePoint vulnerabilities, another flaw beyond the one Microsoft patched this month has reportedly also been exploited.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">美國CISA日前警告駭客正利用三個已知SharePoint漏洞發動攻擊,如今傳出微軟本月修補以外的另一漏洞也遭實際利用。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177382\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#fdeef0;border-left:5px solid #e0738a;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#e0738a;font-weight:800;\">7.</span> 54% of Enterprises Already Hit by an AI Agent Security Incident<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#d83a5e;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">研究</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">54%企業已發生AI代理資安事件,多數仍讓代理共用憑證</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">A survey of 107 enterprises finds more than half have had a confirmed AI agent security incident or near-miss, while only about a third give each agent its own scoped identity.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">一份針對107家企業的調查發現,逾半數已發生AI代理資安事件或差點釀禍,僅約三分之一企業為每個代理設置獨立且受限的身分。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">VentureBeat</b> · <a href=\"https://venturebeat.com/ai/the-agent-security-gap-54-of-enterprises-have-already-had-an-ai-agent-incident-and-most-still-let-agents-share-credentials\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#edeefb;border-left:5px solid #6b72d6;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#6b72d6;font-weight:800;\">8.</span> Why Anthropic Is Pushing States to Regulate AI Faster<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#5159c9;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">政策</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Anthropic為何力推各州加速AI監管腳步</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Anthropic backed landmark AI transparency laws in California and New York last year, but its state policy lead says those rules may already be falling behind fast-moving AI capabilities.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Anthropic去年支持加州與紐約的AI透明度法案,但其州政策負責人表示,這些規範恐已跟不上AI能力的快速發展。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">Wired</b> · <a href=\"https://www.wired.com/story/why-anthropic-is-pushing-states-to-regulate-ai-faster/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#e8f4fb;border-left:5px solid #3f97c9;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#3f97c9;font-weight:800;\">9.</span> EU Orders Google to Open Android AI Features and Share Search Data<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#2b7fb0;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">政策</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">歐盟要求Google開放Android AI功能並共享搜尋資料</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">The European Commission issued two binding rules under the Digital Markets Act requiring Google to open Android's AI interoperability features and share anonymized search data with qualifying rivals.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">歐盟執委會依《數位市場法》發布兩項具法律約束力的規範,要求Google開放Android的AI互通功能,並向符合資格的第三方搜尋服務分享匿名化搜尋資料。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177388\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#f2f6e8;border-left:5px solid #88a83f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#88a83f;font-weight:800;\">10.</span> Moonshot's Upcoming Kimi 3 Expected to Close Gap With Anthropic's Opus 4.8<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#6e8c28;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">模型</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Moonshot新款Kimi 3有望縮小與Anthropic Opus 4.8的差距</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">The Financial Times reports Kimi K3 will be the largest open AI model from China, with a parameter count between 2 trillion and 3 trillion.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">英國金融時報報導,Kimi K3將成為中國規模最大的開源AI模型,參數量介於2兆至3兆之間。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/16/moonshots-upcoming-kimi-3-is-expected-to-close-the-gap-with-anthropics-opus-4-8/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:center;font-size:11.5px;color:#9aa1ad;padding-top:10px;\">由 AI News Digest 從各家 RSS 自動挑選、翻譯並寄送</div>\n</div>\n"}